Name: Chicago Fire
Title: Take a Shot at the King
Desc: Boden, Ritter, Herrmann and Kidd work to take down a politician responsible for a chemical fire.
LongDescription: Boden, Ritter, Herrmann and Kidd work together to take down a local politician responsible for a chemical fire; after his aunt's accident, Gallo worries about their future; Brett steps in to perform Dylan's magic show when he's out of town.
